my-express-app/
│
├── config/
│   └── db.js
│
├── routes/
│   └── api/
│       └── users.js         ✅ All user CRUD routes
│
├── views/
│   └── admin/
│       ├── layouts/
│       │   └── main.ejs
│       └── pages/
│           ├── dashboard.ejs
│           └── users.ejs
│
├── public/
│   └── admin/
│       ├── css/
│       ├── js/
│       └── images/
│
├── server.js
└── package.json





You can now hit these endpoints:

Method	Endpoint	Description
GET	http://localhost:3000/api/users	List all users
GET	http://localhost:3000/api/users/1	Get user by ID
POST	http://localhost:3000/api/users	Create new user
PUT	http://localhost:3000/api/users/1	Update user
DELETE	http://localhost:3000/api/users/1	Delete user